    "description": "Basically I wanted to make something like Warlords Battlecry III but without the basebuilding, as I never found that particularly exciting. i.e. you<br><br>Choose on the map where you want to go, and once you're there<br>You hire troops with your gold or select those you already have in your retinue, I believe those that don't enter the map become fully rested.<br>OK then with the troops you enter a map, fulfil the maps objective and then claim the reward and gear and gold.<br>Once a troop member has enough XP they will increase a level, where they become fully healed and stronger, you can equip a member with some gear eg better weapon/armour or charm<br><br>Controlled with the mouse<br>and WASD (QE)<br><br>Each map has an objective, the objective is one of the following<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Kill everyone<br></li><li>Peregrination<br></li><li>Fetch<br></li><li>Assassinate<br></li><li>Survive<br></li><li>Collect Stuff<br></li><li>Protection<br></li><li>Destroy<br></li><li>Guide</li></ul>",
